    所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable, InputTypeConfigurable, Writer<Tuple2<K,V>>

    public class SequenceFileWriter<K extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable,V extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable>
extends StreamWriterBase<Tuple2<K,V>>
implements InputTypeConfigurable
    A Writer that writes the bucket files as Hadoop SequenceFiles. The input to the BucketingSink must be a Tuple2 of two Hadoop Writables.
